title: NFL Week 2 picks against the spread, BAL-CIN recap (Football 09/14)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by John Breech to break down the Ravens-Bengals game and the latest news and notes around the NFL before Pete Prisco and R.J. White pop on to give their picks against the spread for every single game as well as their SuperContest leans for Week 2.
